HEADWORD: klavier
<hw>klavier</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a stringed instrument that has a
keyboard, especially a piano, harpsichord, or clavichord; also, the
keyboard of such an instrument. Same as <er>clavier</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> clavier.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

